PrecisAmendment to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES which creates a new section intitled "HOME EQUITY ASSISTANCE" (Article 209.97) for the purpose of providing members of the military who are required to relocate with financial compensation in cases where there has been a decrease in the market value of their principal residence.
